# TDD The Right Way

### Project Installation
After downloading the project's code, run:
- composer install
- php bin/console doctrine:database:create -e test
- php bin/console doctrine:schema:create -e test

### Workshop Requirements
- PHP 7.4 or greater
- Environment ready to run a traditional Symfony app
- Any database compatible with Doctrine

Nice to have:
- Ability to run tests through your IDE
